data.description: What a beautiful Lake front, Masonry accent home in Garden Estates. You can tell the builder paid close attention to detail as you walk into the foyer and notice the smooth rounded corners not only on the walls but also on the double trey ceiling in the Master bedroom. You will love the split bedroom plan with both guest bedrooms on the front off the foyer and the Master bedroom off the hallway leading to the family room. The 4th bedroom/ Bonus room with full bath and closet is the only living space upstairs. The Kitchen features granite counter tops, stainless-steel appliances, Whirlpool smooth top stove, whirlpool microwave, Whirlpool dishwasher and a Whirlpool refrigerator, a walk-in pantry, stainless steel double sink, breakfast bar and dining area with double vinyl windows overlooking back yard and lake. The vaulted ceiling great room has recess lighting, ceiling fan and French doors leading to the back deck with rails and has amazing afternoon sun sets.  The first floor Master bedroom has the beautiful double trey ceiling, ceiling fan and full bath featuring tile floors, double sink, walk-in shower and linen closet. Additional features include tile floors in all baths, a front glass storm door, attic storage, 2 car garage with lots of shelving, gutters and added concrete driveway for boat parking. This is a beautifully built home and in a wonderful neighborhood and close to shopping and restaurants. You will love to call this HOME.
